The spike in interest in these digital mental health tools, which appear to vary in quality and scope, isn’t specific to a single company.
Meanwhile, mental health chatbots Wysa and Woebot have also seen usage go up.
So it’s no surprise that people are increasingly flocking to digital mental health services.
Getting to know the different types of digital mental health toolsAmid a pandemic, people are understandably seeking out mental health support online.
Even mental health chatbots are observing growing traffic, almost certainly due to Covid-19.